{"tid":2035204,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB竟然有上季聯賽亞軍利記既贏波精華","createTime":"2020-05-25T17:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T18:34:04.000Z","uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"97fa28b9f38ab886a04f9bc852bd398706d3aed4","tid":2035204,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/05/26/014815_df3782c6716933d88e745e82e34378a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F05%2F26%2F014815_df3782c6716933d88e745e82e34378a0.png&h=89dfa2a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/esABZi8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FesABZi8.png&h=0a5f7fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qUXT1xL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqUXT1xL.png&h=0b8eb7aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BFFa3Mb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBFFa3Mb.png&h=e54fe0a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n愛沙尼亞甲組足球聯賽，利維迪亞3-1反勝圖列維克。<br />\n<br />\n聯賽在3月完成首輪後因疫情暫停，在上周三重開。閉門作賽之下，黃衫、主場的圖列維克37分鐘領先。<br />\n<br />\n利維迪亞是上屆亞軍，維斯沃射門省中人，換邊後2分鐘追平。<br />\n<br />\n當地足總早前讚揚歐洲足協在疫情期間向屬會撥款，拯救了很多球會。<br />\n<br />\n利維迪亞靠基利斯連入兩球，最後反勝3-1，三戰全勝排榜首。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/sports/5ecb8e21335d19e810f1d6d6/%E6%84%9B%E6%B2%99%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9E%E7%94%B2%E7%B5%84%E8%81%AF%E8%B3%BD%E5%9C%96%E5%88%97%E7%B6%AD%E5%85%8B-1-3-%E5%88%A9%E7%B6%AD%E8%BF%AA%E4%BA%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fsports%2F5ecb8e21335d19e810f1d6d6%2F%25E6%2584%259B%25E6%25B2%2599%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E4%25BA%259E%25E7%2594%25B2%25E7%25B5%2584%25E8%2581%25AF%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E5%259C%2596%25E5%2588%2597%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E5%2585%258B-1-3-%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E8%25BF%25AA%25E4%25BA%259E&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY3Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%